Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/pm: Disable SCLK switching on Oland with high pixel
 clocks (v3)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1234429
